{"tid":2398371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警拘3人涉搶元朗女商人5萬元財物　兩被捕青年有黑社會背景","createTime":"2021-02-07T08:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T08:49:35.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c710a08d5f681b41436f41fc9b7c1951b6f64df5","tid":2398371,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T08:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/39900aa0d36274115b49592e5a8a6edd/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210207/_2021020715272411214.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F39900aa0d36274115b49592e5a8a6edd%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210207%2F_2021020715272411214.jpg&h=0ab4583e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方講解案情。<br />\n<br />\n元朗上星期二 (2日)發生一宗搶劫案，一名報稱為商人的女子被3名男子搶去約5萬元財物。警方經深入調查後，於前日(5日)及昨日分別拘捕3名男子，年齡介乎14至20歲，當中兩人有黑社會背景。<br />\n<br />\n元朗警區總督察(刑事)歐陽德表示，上星期二 (2日)凌晨約3時40分，一名中年女子當時行經元朗西菁街，並正前往上班。途中，她被3名男子截停，包括兩名本地男子及一名南亞裔男子。當時，其中一名本地男子手持木棍，而該名南亞裔男子則以廣東話向其聲稱打劫，並要求女事主交出手袋及手機。女事主在受驚下，聽從對方的要求，3人在得手後隨即逃去。經點算後，在被疑犯搶去的手袋中放有5萬元現金及八達通等財物。元朗警區重案組第一隊隨即接手調查。<br />\n<br />\n經翻查附近的閉路電視片段及深入調查後，警方鎖定3名疑犯的身份，並在前日(5日)及昨日進行拘捕行動，分別在天水圍及元朗拘捕3名涉案男子。該兩名被捕的本地男子分別為14及16歲，分別報稱為學生及職侍應，警方相信他們有黑社會背景。另一名被捕的20歲南亞裔男子則持有香港身份證，警方在其住所中檢獲部分失物，包括1.4萬元現金、女事主的手機及八達通。3人將被通宵扣查，並將被控一項行劫罪，明日將在屯門裁判法院提堂。歐陽德續指，女事主報稱為商人，並從事街市生意，又指根據現場附近的閉路電視片段，3名疑犯在大棠路近大馬路一帶已開始跟蹤女事主，並計劃向她進行行劫。他又指，經過2019年的社會事件後，青少年的守法意識薄弱，但重申警方打擊「搵快錢」暴力罪案絕不手軟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/1b186364704da85d5eaba2b0cbf4d638/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210207/_2021020715272582782.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F1b186364704da85d5eaba2b0cbf4d638%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210207%2F_2021020715272582782.jpg&h=215972ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/5e8c3a8f4f954cf826cc083c6170a51f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210207/_2021020715272695795.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F5e8c3a8f4f954cf826cc083c6170a51f%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210207%2F_2021020715272695795.jpg&h=309abc69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/fc591b9bcfbf4c30afc301dd077a1eb2/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210207/_2021020715272764167.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2Ffc591b9bcfbf4c30afc301dd077a1eb2%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210207%2F_2021020715272764167.jpg&h=00925444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/79792bf5c2976441c20022e77b06c609/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210207/_2021020715272999051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F79792bf5c2976441c20022e77b06c609%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210207%2F_2021020715272999051.jpg&h=7b43a957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1994334/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%983%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89%E6%90%B6%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E5%A5%B3%E5%95%86%E4%BA%BA5%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%B2%A1%E7%89%A9-%E5%85%A9%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%89%E9%BB%91%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1994334%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%25983%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%2590%25B6%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2595%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA5%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%2589%25A9-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%25BB%2591%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%2583%258C%25E6%2599%25AF&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=d298b259\" da